<th>Avg Open Rate</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>Urgency</td>
<td>"Ends tonight: 25% off all services"</td>
<td>45-55%</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Local reference</td>
<td>"Best [City] weekend plans + our deal"</td>
<td>40-50%</td>
</tr>
<tr>
